content: Aromahead application is way outdated i just paid money for it.. Hello please update 8/1/2020 . You know there is some really good infomation so I am glad i bought it. Like another reviewer said, "at least its not second hand news". Real advise. It would be great if it was updatedðŸ’¢
Love this app need a few new recipes though....needs to be updated!!!

majorly out of date app. its last update was in February of 2016.. you would think with an app you have to pay for that they would keep it up to date but it doesn't seem like the app is a priority for them at all anymore. For security reasons my phone would not even let me activate it because I guess the security of the app it's so far out of date. All in all not worth it.
It would be nice if you can put the latin name of the EOs in each recipes.
my phone keeps prompting me for an update, wish there was more, but otherwise it's an OK app.
i love it
Nice and easy recipes well worth having

Great recipes. Have used several, & they work. Andrea is a great teacher & this app is a great place to get a recipe from a real aromatherapist instead of all the wannabes posting misinformation & something they THINK might work.
Love the app and the courses Andrea offers at Aromahead Institute! Would be nice to add a link to aromatics international

I would like there to be information on each essential oil used in the recipe and why its there. Even one sentence per ingredient is fine as long as I know what is the benefit of the property and why its there.   For a paid app, this is a bit disappointing since I can easily look up recipes online.. but now I have to look up basic information on each ingredient seperately out of the app.  The recipes are nice and the interface is easy to navigate.

I thought it was an app to help you learn about how to blend oils, their properties, etc. but it's really just a collection of recipes. Unfortunately I don't really feel very confident about these recipes either, because one of them calls for both vinegar and liquid castile soap. Doesn't everyone know that vinegar and castile soap should NEVER be mixed? Can't believe I paid for this.

As a qualified aromatherapy practitioner and instructor, I refer both clients and students to this app all the time.  Andrea is a masterful teacher, and the blends in her app are safe, effective, and beautiful.  Lots of recipe categories means there's something for everyone, beginner to student to expert, for a wide range of blending concerns. It's fun and instructive to study Andrea's blends as a way of developing your own knowledge of aromatherapy.  And for the times you're in a hurry and can't formulate your own, this app is an excellent go-to!
For an app that costs us money i would expect it to have more!! More recipes and information is needed to justify paying for this app. A little disappointed!
Quick and to the point.

I love this app. But I did have a couple of thoughts to improve on it.  1. Just like in the classes at Aromahead Institute, some data info about the oils used in the recipes would be helpful. 2. Have a folder to input our own recipes to keep at hand and for future reference.  3. Have a login to our Aromahead Institute account where we could access the recipes from the classes we have paid for and completed.   If I was a developer I would help but sadly I'm not. I hope this may help for the future.
Fun easy recipes. Include all details needed for tecipes.

Hoping this app gets more info.  If it were free, I'd rate it higher. I wanted untainted, unbiased info from an aromatherapist. Every other app I downloaded felt like they were selling a specific brand (mostly doterra or YL). I don't appreciate the misinformation and misrepresentation from these companies so I don't want their products or their apps. This app, though, does not have much info considering I paid for it.  :( I'm hoping more info gets added over time and it becomes easily searchable.
I reference this app when I'm in a hurry and need a safe and reliable blend or recipe. Thank you for such a great app! Easy to use and is visually very appealing.
Love this!
AWESOME resource!
Awesome app wish we could share it
You can find all these simple recipes online. Not worth spending 2.99.
I'm  very  grateful for the  information.  Thank you
Awesome app

Thank you Aromahead Institute for making this APP available to me! I look over the essential oil recipes every day. The recipes are so easy to understand and useful. I would advise this APP for anyone concerned with healthy options in their lives.
Awesome
Love this. It comes in so handy.
Great info on fast remedies
Love all the recipes
Love it!!
